==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sudarium
<hw>Su*da"ri*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a
handkerchief.]</ety> <fld>(Eccl.)</fld> <def>The handkerchief upon which
the Savior is said to have impressed his own portrait miraculously, when
wiping his face with it, as he passed to the crucifixion.</def><-- =
Veronica's veil. -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sudary</ent>⟦br⟧
